{"tid":1960676,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民建聯批電子點票久未落實　倡長者公務人員優先投票","createTime":"2020-04-06T09:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T11:41:40.000Z","uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"14ea2a747b678a038e6ceea99d9f8d94690c64d3","tid":1960676,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:52:07.000Z","msg":"電子點票同長者公務人員優先投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20200406/s00001/11e94ce593cc5c5f78071bd2ef9a04a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20200406%2Fs00001%2F11e94ce593cc5c5f78071bd2ef9a04a4.jpg&h=2ada6138&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民建聯主席李慧琼、副主席張國鈞今日（6日）在線上記者會表示，對立法會選舉活動建議指引非常不滿，批評選管會未能針對在去年區選發生的暴力及選舉不公問題。他們提出幾點建議，包括要求當局安排長者和當日要執行職務的公務人員如警察、票站職員優先投票；要求局方跟進為何電子點票安排籌備經年，至近日才說因為反修例風波和疫情而未能做到。<br />\n<br />\n選管會早前建議，參加政黨內部遴選者，均屬「候選人」。李慧琼說，選舉法例目的應是支持選舉發展，而不是製造障礙予政黨和參選人，政府早前說相關指引無更改，過去亦無任何參選人因參加黨內初選而受挑戰，希望今次處理方法一致。<br />\n<br />\n張國鈞表示，政制及內地事務局長聶德權曾說，9月立法會選舉會在適合的功能組別做電子點票，惟近日政府回覆說，因反修例風波和疫情影響招標工作，未能做到電子點票；又說在地方選區600多個票站均安裝點票機，並不符合成本效益。李慧琼認為政府說法不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n他們又建議市民在票站外排隊時，就用身分證號碼作分流。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200406/s00001/1586161715574/民建聯批電子點票久未落實-倡長者公務人員優先投票\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200406%2Fs00001%2F1586161715574%2F%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E6%89%B9%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E9%BB%9E%E7%A5%A8%E4%B9%85%E6%9C%AA%E8%90%BD%E5%AF%A6-%E5%80%A1%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%84%AA%E5%85%88%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLVDf25aqCgCAAhwKlvpwqyI%3D&h=72ab2f49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200406%2Fs00001%2F1586161715574%2F%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E6%89%B9%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E9%BB%9E%E7%A5%A8%E4%B9%85%E6%9C%AA%E8%90%BD%E5%AF%A6-%E5%80%A1%E9%95%B7%E8%80%85%E5%85%AC%E5%8B%99%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%84%AA%E5%85%88%E6%8A%95%E7%A5%A8&h=e78b66e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200406/s00001/1586161715574/民建聯批電子點票久未落實-倡長者公務人員優先投票</a>"},{"pid":"5326a356d8b15e3c2b498fe4a482ddd3abcb74a4","tid":1960676,"uid":200858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:54:53.000Z","msg":"年齡歧視？<br />\n職業歧視？"},{"pid":"16fd5b27eaaaaa473015565a2ef81d4306384a80","tid":1960676,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T09:58:16.000Z","msg":"電子點票咪可以種票<br />\n唔可以俾廢老投先<br />\n大家都公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46ac99e8113d44fda12aa86b2b6013e8eda15393","tid":1960676,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:25:32.000Z","msg":"票站外分開排隊咪即係公開自己私隱？<br />\n舊年我嗰區要Y字頭分開排<br />\n有個票站職員仲大大聲嗌Y5後入嚟啦<br />\n當場俾我屌柒佢無腦"},{"pid":"33fbccb43c1303b38632d6aab3f5c0cf012ee0dd","tid":1960676,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T11:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}